494
00:37:11.639 --> 00:37:13.909
<i>Maaari kang bumalik kahit kailan mo gusto.</i>

495
00:37:13.909 --> 00:37:17.522
<i>May pamilya ka rin dito.</i>

496
00:37:18.187 --> 00:37:19.580
