540
00:40:55.360 --> 00:40:58.014
Mukhang hindi na tayo matutulog agad.

541
00:40:58.014 --> 00:41:00.047
Nilibang namin ang aming mga sarili sa pamamagitan ng pag-uusap.

542
00:41:04.008 --> 00:41:05.865
Hindi mo ba sila kukunin?

543
00:41:05.865 --> 00:41:07.654
Meron pa.

544
00:41:12.361 --> 00:41:14.927
- Kalusugan.
- Kalusugan.

545
00:41:20.107 --> 00:41:21.928
Binabati kita.

546
00:41:21.928 --> 00:41:24.105
