Ang sabaw dito ay kahanga-hanga.

584
00:44:36.547 --> 00:44:37.716
Oh talaga?

585
00:44:37.716 --> 00:44:39.542
Umupo tayo dito.

586
00:44:41.656 --> 00:44:43.253
Jun Kyung?

587
